# ThreatDefender Tools - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values

# Azure AD App Registration (for MSAL authentication)
# Required for Sentinel workspace/incident lookup feature
REACT_APP_AZURE_CLIENT_ID=your-azure-ad-app-client-id

# The Azure AD App Registration needs the following API permissions:
# - Microsoft Graph: User.Read (delegated)
# - Azure Service Management: user_impersonation (delegated)
# - Log Analytics API: Data.Read (delegated)
#
# These permissions allow the app to:
# 1. Read user profile information
# 2. List Azure subscriptions and Sentinel workspaces
# 3. Fetch incident details from Microsoft Sentinel
# 4. Run Log Analytics queries for incident-related logs
